               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_746"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_baecker_QGW_II_I_746">Nichlas, der <roleName type="prof">pekch</roleName>, gesessen in der Chruegstrass</rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__katharina_QGW_II_I_746_a">Katrei, seine <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__niklas_baecker_QGW_II_I_746">Hausfrau</roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__dietrich_baecker_QGW_II_I_746">Dietreich der <roleName type="prof">pekch</roleName>, sein <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__niklas_baecker_QGW_II_I_746">pru/eder</roleName>, gesessen
